comments: VanVleet (TOR) moves over the top of the pick and marginal contact occurs with Drummond (PHI).  The reaction from Drummond is not consistent with the contact from VanVleet.
Drummond (PHI) is already in Anunoby's (TOR) path when contact occurs and he releases away from the contact.
Anunoby (TOR) applies a rested forearm to Harris' (PHI) side and marginal contact occurs during his driving shot attempt.
Barnes (TOR) holds Drummond's (PHI) arm during rebounding.
Barnes (TOR) maintains verticality and marginal contact occurs as Drummond (PHI) cuts back towards the rim.
Achiuwa (TOR) establishes himself in a screening position in Curry's (PHI) path and is firming up when contact occurs.
Replay review of the foul called on Drummond (PHI) pursuant to a coach's challenge was deemed successful.  Drummond cleanly blocks Achiuwa's (TOR) shot at the rim.
Achiuwa (TOR) establishes himself in a screening position in Harris' (PHI) path and releases away from the contact.
Curry (PHI) makes marginal contact with Trent Jr.'s (TOR) arm after the release of his jump shot attempt.
VanVleet (TOR) applies a rested forearm to Korkmaz's (PHI) front and marginal contact occurs as Korkmaz is gathering the ball.
Anunoby (TOR) places his forearm to Drummond's (PHI) front and marginal contact occurs as he defends the shot attempt.
Drummond (PHI) and Anunoby (TOR) briefly engage and disengage as they attempt to secure the rebound.
Barnes (TOR) is already in Korkmaz's (PHI) path when contact occurs and he does not deliver contact.
Trent Jr. (TOR) is already in Drummond's (PHI) path and is firming up when contact occurs.
Harris (PHI) applies a rested hand to Anunoby's (TOR) front at the end of his drive and marginal contact occurs as he is passing the ball.
Niang (PHI) establishes himself in a screening position in Barnes' (TOR) path and is firming up when contact occurs.
Anunoby (TOR) applies a rested forearm to Harris' (PHI) side and marginal contact occurs during the driving shot attempt.
Harris (PHI) commits a take foul on VanVleet (TOR).
Harris (PHI) commits a take foul on Anunoby (TOR).
Niang (PHI) establishes himself in a screening position in VanVleet's (TOR) path and does not deliver contact.
